{"tid":1083591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享一個生物小知識","createTime":"2019-03-29T17:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T05:35:34.000Z","uid":124147,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7b54b60b26f1ae3e828ec768cdb7ba24676cea","tid":1083591,"uid":124147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:16:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>You Almost Certainly Have Mites On Your Face - National Geographic</strong><br />\n<br />\n蠕形蟎屬（學名：Demodex），又稱毛囊蟎或毛囊蟲，亦即俗稱的「蟎蟲」，是小型寄生蟎類的一個屬。 常寄生於哺乳動物的毛囊內。目前已知蠕形蟎有約65個種，140多個亞種；它們都是最小的節肢動物。目前已知有兩種寄生於人類：毛囊蠕形蟎與皮脂腺蠕形蟎，常被稱作「睫毛蟎」（eyelash mites）。蠕形蟎的感染非常常見，幾乎所有人類都有，患者一般也不會出現任何症狀；蠕形蟎偶爾會引發某些皮膚疾病。狗隻身上也有蟎蟲寄生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/蠕形蟎屬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%A0%95%E5%BD%A2%E8%9F%8E%E5%B1%AC&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7c0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=5ef941a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/蠕形蟎屬</a><br />\n<br />\n通過皮膚問題就可以大概判定出來，大量的蠕形蟎常常會帶來這些變化：<br />\n<br />\n1、皮膚粗糙、起屑。蠕形蟎雖然肉眼看不見，但它們有著鋒利的爪子、嘴和刺，慢慢的啃食皮膚、劃傷皮膚，造成皮膚粗糙、起屑，敷面膜、去角質後過幾天又變粗糙了。<br />\n<br />\n2、毛孔粗大。蠕形蟎堵塞在毛孔里會讓毛孔越來越大，大多數人用很多護膚品都沒辦法縮小。<br />\n<br />\n3、臉部出油多。毛孔里的皮脂腺如果被刺激，就會不停的出油，油脂可是蟎蟲最愛的食物，因此它們會分泌一種酵素，刺激皮脂腺。<br />\n<br />\n4、毛孔堵塞，黑頭除不完。蠕形蟎刺激皮膚出油，又會堵塞在毛孔里，導致油脂排不出去，引發黑頭粉刺，如果沒有清除蠕形蟎，黑頭就會拔完又長。<br />\n<br />\n5、睡覺起來冒痘痘，好的很慢。蟎蟲在夜間最為活躍，會進出毛孔，進食、交配、繁殖等，給毛孔帶入很多皮膚表面的細菌，如果毛孔堵塞，細菌就會大量繁殖，造成毛孔發炎、長痘，這樣的痘痘因為蠕形蟎的存在而反覆難好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://eyelovecares.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/050517-skin-gross-1-e1538082618353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feyelovecares.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F050517-skin-gross-1-e1538082618353.jpg&h=5abedae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAre you lonely? Don&rsquo;t be <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce356890051d879828eb3288f881f5308223055","tid":1083591,"uid":95637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"點樣殺曬佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872c12a2e67cde07d075cfa3378eeb351de35e2a","tid":1083591,"uid":154892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e9b665990cb4e20b2db0e5c9cce5646324f48d","tid":1083591,"uid":124147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ce356890051d879828eb3288f881f5308223055","tid":1083591,"uid":95637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"點樣殺曬佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.medpartner.club/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/臉上蟎蟲_治療.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medpartner.club%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F%E8%87%89%E4%B8%8A%E8%9F%8E%E8%9F%B2_%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82.png&h=725e3c5d&s={SIZE}\" />我知道左之後噁心左成個下晝<br />\npo出黎同大家開心share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326a1723b0af298f002e827a6e85c3cf0c52508a","tid":1083591,"uid":124147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a08ac9d0f4603fc573054435c2b53a263e1c6dc","tid":1083591,"uid":124147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}